隨便詢問任何攝影人士，所有的答案都是：不用懷疑，摩洛哥是世上數一數二適合攝影的場景。本週，澳洲籍部落客[Moroccan
Meanderings](http://moroccanmeanderings.blogspot.com/2007/06/morocco-
snapshots.html "http://moroccanmeanderings.blogspot.com/2007/06/morocco-
snapshots.html")即選擇以照片代替文字，告訴我們：

> 由於我的部落格照片得到許多正面迴響，因此我想多分享一些關於摩洛哥的照片。

[![dades_gorge1.jpeg](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/dades_gorge1.jpeg)](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/dades_gorge1.jpeg "dades_gorge1.jpeg")

上圖攝於摩洛哥東南方的[達德斯谷地(Dades Gorges)](http://www.answers.com/Dades%20Gorge
"http://www.answers.com/Dades%20Gorge")，風景美不勝收，部落客[Wakha](http://wakha.blogspot.com/2006/08/fishermans-
life.html "http://wakha.blogspot.com/2006/08/fishermans-
life.html")分享一張蘇維拉(Essaouira)壯麗美景照片，並附上一段引述，圖文相得益彰：

[![Essaouira by Lindsey Ludwig from Wakha
Blog](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/essaouira.jpg)](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/essaouira.jpg "Essaouira by Lindsey Ludwig from Wakha
Blog") **感謝Lindsey Ludwig提供照片**

> 「我自己似乎又在裏邊又在外邊，對這幕人生悲喜劇無窮的演變，又是陶醉又是噁心。」 ──費茲傑羅(F. Scott Fitzgerald)

一如前圖，摩洛哥天際早已是攝影人士慣用的主題，[The Morocco
Report](http://www.moroccosavvy.com/taamarbuuta/2007/06/09/this-is-where-i-
live/ "http://www.moroccosavvy.com/taamarbuuta/2007/06/09/this-is-where-i-
live/")帶領我們前往遠在北方的城市梅克尼斯(Meknes)，欣賞摩洛哥澄空的另種風情。

[![Photo by Jillian York, Meknes,
Morocco](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/moroccoreportsky.jpg)](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/moroccoreportsky.jpg "Photo by Jillian York, Meknes,
Morocco")

摩洛哥不但以澄澈天空著名，當地的藝術品如地毯等，也相當引人入勝，[My
Marrakesh](http://moroccanmaryam.typepad.com/my_marrakesh/2007/06/marrakesh_and_c.html
"http://moroccanmaryam.typepad.com/my_marrakesh/2007/06/marrakesh_and_c.html")的
Maryam與我們分享一些色彩斑斕的摩洛哥珍品：

[![Objets d’art by My Marrakesh](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/maryam.JPG)](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/maryam.JPG "Objets d’art by My Marrakesh")

本週最後一張照片帶領我們來到即將閉幕的[費斯摩洛哥宗教音樂嘉年華(Fes Festival of World Sacred
Music)](http://www.fesfestival.com/ "http://www.fesfestival.com/")，部落客[Long
Way Home](http://scarlettscion.blogspot.com/2007/06/week-in-pictures.html
"http://scarlettscion.blogspot.com/2007/06/week-in-
pictures.html")分享了部份嘉年華的照片，今年的活動成功展現多元文化，我特別喜愛其中表演葛利果聖歌的團體：

[![Fes Festival by Long Way Home - Gregorian
Chants](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/fesfestival.JPG)](https://www.globalvoicesonline.org/wp-
content/uploads/2007/06/fesfestival.JPG "Fes Festival by Long Way Home -
Gregorian Chants")

